sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Gateway
    participant Proxy as Sidecar Proxy<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant SSRF as AllowlistValidator<br/>(In-process)
    participant Prefiller as Remote vLLM Prefiller<br/>Dynamic Port HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Decoder as Local vLLM Decoder<br/>8001/TCP HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXL v2)

    Client->>Proxy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Header: x-prefiller-host-port<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Proxy->>SSRF: Validate prefiller target<br/>against InferencePool allowlist
    SSRF-->>Proxy: Allowed (or 403 Forbidden)

    Note over Proxy,Prefiller: Prefill Phase
    Proxy->>Prefiller: Modified request:<br/>kv_transfer_params.do_remote_decode=true<br/>stream=false, max_tokens=1<br/>Header: x-request-id (UUID)
    Prefiller-->>Proxy: Response with kv_transfer_params:<br/>remote_engine_id, block_ids,<br/>host, port

    Note over Proxy,Decoder: Decode Phase
    Proxy->>Decoder: Original request +<br/>kv_transfer_params from prefiller<br/>(original stream/max_tokens restored)<br/>Header: x-request-id (UUID)
    Decoder-->>Proxy: Inference response<br/>(streaming or complete)
    Proxy-->>Client: Response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Passthrough (No Disaggregation)

    Client->>Proxy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(no x-prefiller-host-port header)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Proxy->>Decoder: Forward request directly<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8001/TCP
    Decoder-->>Proxy: Inference response
    Proxy-->>Client: Response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
